    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can just change the project structure to add that folder as a \"source\" directory.</p>\n\n<p><em>Project Structure → Modules →</em> Click the <code>generated-sources</code> folder and make it a <code>sources</code> folder.</p>\n\n<p>Or:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;plugin&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.codehaus.mojo&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;build-helper-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.4&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;executions&gt;\n        &lt;execution&gt;\n            &lt;id&gt;test&lt;/id&gt;\n            &lt;phase&gt;generate-sources&lt;/phase&gt;\n            &lt;goals&gt;\n                &lt;goal&gt;add-source&lt;/goal&gt;\n            &lt;/goals&gt;\n            &lt;configuration&gt;\n                &lt;sources&gt;\n                    &lt;source&gt;${basedir}/target/generated-sources&lt;/source&gt;\n                &lt;/sources&gt;\n            &lt;/configuration&gt;\n        &lt;/execution&gt;\n    &lt;/executions&gt;\n&lt;/plugin&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
