    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>With gradle, the project settings will be cleared whenever you refresh the gradle settings. Instead you need to add the following lines (or similar) in your build.gradle, I'm using kotlin so:</p>\n\n<pre><code>sourceSets {\n    main {\n        java {\n            srcDir \"${buildDir.absolutePath}/generated/source/kapt/main\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
