      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "The word &quot;automatically&quot; imply that Intellj do it without user interaction. This isn&#39;t true. There is always the need to click the &quot;Generate Sources And Update Folders&quot; button each time IntelliJ decide to wipe the sources or/and resources. Wiping them work automatically, but reimporting the project not. This behavior is really annoying."
