    "answer_id" : 46812593,
    "question_id" : 5170620,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'm using Maven (Spring Boot application). Solution is:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Right click project folder</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Maven</strong></li>\n<li>Select <strong>Generate Sources And Update Folders</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Then, IntelliJ automatically imports generated sources to project.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "user_type" : "does_not_exist",
