      "body" : "I fixed it like this: 1. Close IDEA. 2. Backup <code>.idea</code> folder. 3. Reopen project in IDEA and wait until it finished loading. 4. Close IDEA. 5. Restore original <code>.idea</code> folder. 6. Reopen project in IDEA. \uD83E\uDD37‍♀️"
