    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>i ran mvn generate-resources and then marked the /target/generated-resources folder as &quot;sources&quot; (Project Structure -&gt; Project Settings -&gt; Modules -&gt; Select /target/generated-resources -&gt; Click on blue &quot;Sources&quot; icon.</p>\n"
