    "answer_id" : 67739160,
    "question_id" : 5170620,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For someone still struggle to fix the generated source not picking up by IntelliJ,</p>\n<p>One reason could be the generated file size too big for it to load, then you need to put following line into your &quot;custom IntelliJ IDEA properties&quot; (under menu help)</p>\n<pre><code>idea.max.intellisense.filesize=7500\n</code></pre>\n"
